The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Metro Recommends

 THE TV SHOW 

 (Discovery Channel, 9 pm, September 18)A detailed look at the natural disaster that shook America. Watch scientists examine the life cycle of Katrina, its destruction potential and the pioneering technique used to give out the evacuation warning that saved lives.

 THE FEST

 (Nandan II, 3 pm and 5 pm, September 23-25)

 Day I features Mainichi ga Natsuyasumi and Gakko no Kaidan; Tsuri Baka Nisshi 3 and Sensei Ashita Harerukana will be screened on Day II; the concluding day shows Tsuru and Hashi no Nai Kawa. 

 THE DISPLAY

 (Artisana, 10 am-7.30 pm, September 21-25)

 Organised by Crafts Council of West Bengal, the exhibition showcases a range of jamdani saris in designs revived from the past.




